conboy (0.5.0) stable; urgency=low

  * Added full text search
  * Added settings dialog
  * Added setting to switch between small and large scroll bars
  * Added setting to show note window or search window on startup
  * Added settings to change colors
  * Added support for portrait mode in Fremantle
  * Added italian translation (Thanks to debernardis)
  * Updated the UI for Fremantle
  * Updated french translation (Thanks to fpp) 
  * Bug fixes
  
 -- Cornelius Hald <hald@icandy.de>  Sat, 27 Jun 2009 20:13:14 +0200  

conboy (0.4.5) stable; urgency=low

  * Added support for tags. Tags aka Notebooks are now preserved.
  * Added french translation. Thanks to fpp.
  * Added support for JSON serialization.
  * Note version and note content version are no longer hardcoded.
  * Added support for JSON deserialization.
 
 -- Cornelius Hald <hald@icandy.de>  Mo, 5 Jun 2009 17:41:12 +0200 

